OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny evening
OL,6,Fshowers will fade this evening, with
OL,7,Fmost places staying dry but turning
OL,8,Fcloudier across the northeast. An
OL,9,Feasterly breeze will gradually develop
OL,10,Fovernight, drawing in fresher air into
OL,11,Feastern areas. Staying rather warm in
OL,12,Fthe southwest.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FDry for most with sunny
OL,15,Fspells. Cloudier in the northeast with
OL,16,Fbright spells developing. Perhaps the
OL,17,Fodd shower in the west. Very warm in
OL,18,Fthe southwest, but feeling fresher
OL,19,Felsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
